        <section id="overview">
            <h2>üìã Overview</h2>
            <p>Gmail Smart Cleaner ("the Extension") is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains what data we collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding your data.</p>
            
            <p><strong>Extension Purpose:</strong> Gmail Smart Cleaner safely archives Gmail emails with a preview feature and 30-second undo functionality.</p>
            
            <p><strong>Data Philosophy:</strong> We collect the absolute minimum data necessary to provide our service. Your data stays on your device.</p>

            <div class="highlight">
                <strong>‚úì Key Points:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>No passwords stored (OAuth 2.0 used)</li>
                    <li>All data stored locally on your device</li>
                    <li>Data NOT transmitted to external servers</li>
                    <li>Full user control over your data</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="section-divider"></div>

        <section id="what-we-collect">
            <h2>üìä What Data We Collect</h2>

            <h3>1. Email Address & Display Name</h3>
            <p><span class="check">‚úì COLLECTED</span></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Your Gmail address (e.g., user@gmail.com)</li>
                <li>Your display name from Gmail profile</li>
                <li>Used to display greeting: "Hi [Name]"</li>
                <li>Confirms correct account is logged in</li>
                <li>Stored locally, never transmitted</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>2. OAuth Access Token</h3>
            <p><span class="warning">‚ö† COLLECTED (Secure)</span></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Generated by Google, NOT a password</li>
                <li>Authorizes Gmail API requests</li>
                <li>Expires automatically after 1 hour</li>
                <li>Users can revoke anytime</li>
                <li>Stored encrypted in local extension storage</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>3. Email Metadata (List View Only)</h3>
            <p><span class="check">‚úì COLLECTED</span></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Sender information</li>
                <li>Email subject lines</li>
                <li>Email dates</li>
                <li><span class="cross">‚úó NOT</span> email body content</li>
                <li><span class="cross">‚úó NOT</span> attachments</li>
                <li><span class="cross">‚úó NOT</span> full message text</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>4. Extension Settings & Preferences</h3>
            <p><span class="check">‚úì COLLECTED</span></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Your settings choices (toggles, preferences)</li>
                <li>UI state (which screen you're viewing)</li>
                <li>Undo timer state (30-second countdown)</li>
                <li>All stored locally only</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Data NOT Collected</h3>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Data Type</th>
                        <th>Status</th>
                        <th>Why</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Passwords</td>
                        <td><span class="cross">‚úó NOT collected</span></td>
                        <td>OAuth 2.0 used instead</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Health Information</td>
                        <td><span class="cross">‚úó NOT collected</span></td>
                        <td>Not applicable to extension</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Financial Data</td>
                        <td><span class="cross">‚úó NOT collected</span></td>
                        <td>No payments involved</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Location/IP Address</td>
                        <td><span class="cross">‚úó NOT collected</span></td>
                        <td>No location services used</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Browser History</td>
                        <td><span class="cross">‚úó NOT collected</span></td>
                        <td>Extension doesn't monitor web</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Keystroke Logging</td>
                        <td><span class="cross">‚úó NOT collected</span></td>
                        <td>No keyboard monitoring</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Analytics/Tracking</td>
                        <td><span class="cross">‚úó NOT collected</span></td>
                        <td>No tracking pixels or tags</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
